Inherited code notice

This project is a ground-up rewrite of SRLabs' blue-merle
(https://github.com/srlabs/blue-merle) for different hardware. The
design and threat model originate there, and the following file is
derived from blue-merle source code:

  files/lib/blue-merle/luhn.lua
    Derived from blue-merle's files/lib/blue-merle/luhn.lua, which is
    itself adapted from the Luhn checksum implementation published at
    https://cybersecurity.att.com/blogs/labs-research/luhn-checksum-algorithm-lua-implementation

